{"type": "article", "id": 26355, "title": "像点燃蜡烛一样的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-04T07:19:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144020fRWoNFl5dMYka9gX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款 <a href=\"http://www.fosterandpartners.com/\">Foster + Partners</a> 为米兰的照明品牌 <a href=\"http://www.lumina.it/\" target=\"_blank\">Lumina</a> 设计的 EVA 台灯不光在外形上带来惊喜，对光源的设计也让人眼前一亮。在圆柱形的玻璃外壳中，底部装有一个面光源（COB）的 LED 灯， 经过顶部圆锥体的反射，散发出温暖的光芒，整体的造型看起来就好像在玻璃罩中点燃一根蜡烛。另一个比较有意思的细节则是台灯底部传感器，它其实是调光器，可以通过滑动自由调节亮度。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144018lPpMsycjXiozx0mr.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144018P4LxXFlS8pCWEDtV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144019pfMdgotCAhrzR4iK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144019V7CdboIgFtU4BL5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}